PropertyGroupSchedule
public class NonOverlappingTimeSpanSet
extends TimeSpanSet

A Collection which implements a set of TimeSpan elements which are maintained sorted first by start time and then by end time. The order of temporally-equivalent but non-equal objects is undefined but stable.
